    <div class = "question-area">
      <h4 class="qanda_header"> More Information About Us</h4>
      <p class = "questions"> What is Ace Club in detail and what does ACE Stand For? </p>
      <p class = "answer"> Ace Club is the Attitude Chracter and Education Club. This club helps teach <br>
                           younger children in kindergarten, first grade, and second grade about different character<br>
                           values. </p>
      <p class ="questions"> How do we do it? <p>
      <p class = "answer"> We do this by going to the same 6 classes in each grade every month to teach a <br>
                          specific value. We use activities books and other resources to be able to do this. <br>
                           We also use kids who attend the club to help teach.</p>
      <p class="questions"> Why we do it?</p>
      <p class = "answer">We do this because we believe that it is very important for character valuest to be cultivated<br>
                          in young children from a very young age. These values will help the children for there whole<br>
                          life by making them well behaved in the long run.</p>
      <p class="questions"> How we are connected to Character?</p>
      <p class = "answer">We connect to character because we help chidlren with their character for the future.<br>
                          We influence mainly the character of our future generation. This is important because <br>
                          this will shape our future.</p>

